headline: General Dynamics (GD): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q1 Earnings?
summary: General Dynamics’s 11.9% return over the past six months has outpaced the S&P 500 by 6.7%, and its stock price has climbed to $300.75 per share. This performance may have investors wondering how to approach the situation.
